#### ============================================================
#### FINAL INVERTEBRATE BARRIER MODELS
####
#### Fits two Bayesian multilevel models:
####   1. Taxon richness model
####   2. Proportion of non-native taxa model
####
#### Expected input files:
####   - invert_richness_final_barrier_type_reduced.rds
####   - invert_prop_final_barrier_type_reduced.rds
#### ============================================================


#### 1. Packages and settings ------------------------------------

